間房暖啲<br />\n點知連埋佢啲腳味一齊焗<br />\n成間房啲空氣蘊含住腳味<br />\n哇屌你老母臭撚到我想嘔<br />\n之後幾日都形成間房有味<br />\n搞到我食唔到野食乜嘔乜"},{"pid":"053117be31b1673ab2e5b484f86d651ef64cd249","tid":669804,"uid":185947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"我明呀 樓主啲撚樣著鞋唔著襪 隻腳真係纏繞霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次有個朋友黎我屋企 我老母一返黎臭撚到佢即刻返入房唔敢出黎 之後我叫佢洗去洗腳啦 佢用我個浴缸洗完 我浴缸都臭埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搞到佢走左我要拖地同洗浴缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2e8520792129bc90013a79917a6c0596dc644b","tid":669804,"uid":31180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72a1e4cc10024fab8cfd40fe8ba9ea65bf05ec4","tid":669804,"uid":140802,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"58e8374521065b672a2b4d40ba994c1601355bdd","tid":669804,"uid":61903,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37cd4437e9a02226851574f769a9b280de935353","tid":669804,"uid":101485,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T20:03:12.000Z","msg":"香港腳係係咁 沖完涼d水唔抹乾10秒就有腐臭味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:53:21.000Z","msg":"樓主仲要訓喺香港腳踩過既位<br />\n啲真菌&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:55:45.000Z","msg":"香港頭<br />\n會甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"屌你地啦 乜撚野香港頭呀<br />\nBtw真菌上頭會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d6ec703c89f11ab394cf93e27a78378b78d2a6","tid":669804,"uid":44725,"li